name: Hominidae
description: Great apes including humans, chimpanzees, gorillas, and orangutans

name: Cercopithecidae
description: Old World monkeys including macaques, baboons, and langurs

name: Atelidae
description: Howler monkeys, spider monkeys, and woolly monkeys

name: Cebidae
description: New World monkeys including capuchins and squirrel monkeys

name: Felidae
description: Cats including lions, tigers, and domestic cats

name: Canidae
description: Dogs including wolves, foxes, and jackals

name: Muridae
description: True mice and rats, gerbils, spiny mice

name: Cricetidae
description: Hamsters, voles, lemmings, New World rats and mice
